node_1756710896909	76255dc9-84b9-4d63-b725-eb72136128f9	question	Inform your staff that that personal data protection policies and operating guidelines must be read and followed.\nLet the staff know that it is every staff's responsibility to know what actions to take to protect the personal data that they are handling.\nMake every staff understand that they must attend regular training and awareness programmes.	\N	\N	\N	2025-09-01 07:23:57.284348+00	2025-11-15 09:36:21.867474+00	-135	1073	\N	f	1	1	\N	8e513ec086760d4fb084cfe8a15d561e9fb4cca39065501de6bdd808e6317d61	master
